text: Evadne is a name from Greek mythology. Evadne may also refer to: *Evadne (crustacean), a genus of water fleas *HMS Evadne, a converted yacht launched in 1931 People with the given name: *Evadne Baker (1937–1995), South African actress *Evadne Price (1888–1985), Australian-British writer, actress, and media personality *Evadne de Silva, Sri Lankan politician ==See also== *
title: Evadne (disambiguation)
